snippet.title: Total Vice Let’s Play - 3DO M2 Konami - Video Game Esoterica - EP 4.2
snippet.description:
On this weeks episode of Video Game Esoterica we have the full playthrough of Total Vice with and without commentary for everyone!

This is the first time Total Vice has been seen on YouTube or anywhere else as a full playthrough, and we genuinely hope you enjoy it! It was super fun being able to bring this to you all.

Thanks for watching and check back next week for some more M2 content! You can follow us on Instagram @ ChicagoGameCollector. Questions? Comments? Just leave them below and I will do my best to answer each and every one of you!

VGE
